media:group.media:title: China’s Secret Youth Rebellion
media:group.media:description:
China's youth are fed up with communism and despite the tight censorship in China, they're finding secret ways to protest the Chinese Communist Party. in this episode of China Uncensored, we discuss some of the ways they're protesting, why China's youth are especially fed up with the CCP, and why Gen Zers rebelling is a really bad sign for China's communist leaders. 

The Death of China Uncensored? https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=i8xelajthM0
